<span id="freeTextContainer5945513543712998380">I had a very difficult time with this highly rated novel. The writing was very good at times, but other times I felt it would benefit from a strong edit. If you are looking for a light, quick read-this certainly is not the book. Unfortunately, I didn&apos;t love any of the characters in either the contemporary or the historical story. Lots of readers loved this one, I just was not one. </span>
